TypeSignature.Value: .class public auto ansi sealed ChartHatchStyle extends System.Enum

summary.span: 指定圖表項目的影線樣式。

span.span: Specifies a hatching style for a chart element.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 列舉，代表可用於許多圖表元素，例如影線樣式， ，依此類推。The enumeration represents the hatching styles that can be used for numerous chart elements, such as the , , and so forth. 設定`BackHatchStyle`[無] 除外這個列舉型別的任何成員的圖表項目物件的屬性會使對應的影線樣式套用至圖表項目。Setting the `BackHatchStyle` property of a chart element object to any member of this enumeration except None will cause the corresponding hatching style to be applied to the chart element.
